snippet.textDisplay: @pelletier1986 peace man, what your doing is great. I find that if you give a kid a fond memory of an old game, they will return to it in later life, and realise that old games rock loads. I mean i first played mario 64 back in 2000 when i was 5, that got me into nintendo, which in turn (due to their extensive history) got me into retro gaming, and now i can appreciate a game reguardless of it age :D so keep it up!
